column2: select  p.objID,p.mode,p.nChild,p.type,p.clean,p.probPSF,p.insideMask,p.flags,  p.ra,p.dec,  p.dered_u,p.dered_g,p.dered_r,p.dered_i,p.dered_z,  z.objID as objid_photz, z.z as photz, z.zErr as zphoterr, z.nnCount, z.nnVol, z.photoErrorClass,  s.z as zspec, s.zerr as zspecerr, s.zwarning as zspecwarning, s.class as specclass, s.subclass as specsubclass   from PhotoObjAll as p      left outer join Photoz as z on p.objID = z.objID      left outer join SpecObjAll as s on p.specobjID = s.specobjID     left outer join sdssBestTarget2Sector as t on p.ObjID = t.ObjID     left outer join PhotoObjDR7 as r7 on p.ObjID = r7.dr8objid where p.mode = # and s.zwarning = #  into mydb.sdss_all_small_dr1#
